WEBVTT

00:02.134 --> 00:03.726
Previously on The Vampire Diaries:

00:03.902 --> 00:06.496
For over a century,
I have lived in secret. Until now.

00:06.672 --> 00:08.537
I know the risk,
but I have to know her.

00:08.707 --> 00:10.675
Elena. She's a dead ringer
for Katherine.

00:10.843 --> 00:13.073
- What are you?
- I'm a vampire.

00:13.312 --> 00:15.872
I've been 17 years old since 1864.

00:16.081 --> 00:19.312
I promise I will keep your secret,
but I can't be with you, Stefan.

00:19.485 --> 00:22.147
- Five bodies all drained of blood.
- They've come back.

00:22.321 --> 00:24.186
- Hello, brother.
- Damon.

00:25.691 --> 00:27.158
She's transitioning.

00:27.326 --> 00:28.486
- Into what?
- A vampire.

00:28.660 --> 00:30.059
Vicki, what the hell?

00:31.330 --> 00:34.094
- Why does everybody die on me
- Can you make him forget?

00:34.299 --> 00:36.927
- What do you want him to know?
- That Vicki left town.

00:37.102 --> 00:40.401
He's gonna miss her,
but he knows it's for the best.

